profile_interview_audio::title: Gaafannoo Nama Dhuunfaa
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_9::go: Sagalee bakka taatichi guyyicha itti raawwatu waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_3::go: Sagalee yeroo taatichi guyyichaaf qophaa'uu waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_10::g: Sagalee taatichi jireenyasaa keessatti namoota biroo wajjin wal quunnamu waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_4::go: Sagalee bakka taatichaaf barbaachisaa ta'ee waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_13::g: Sagalee waan qaamichaaf barbaachisummaa qabuu waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_12::g: Gaafadhu: Waa'ee gara fuulduraakee nutti himuu dandeessaa?
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_5::go: Gaafadhu: Itti fuftee waa'ee waan hojjettuu nutti himuu dandeessaa?
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_6::go: Waan qaamichi hojjetu kan seenaakeef barbaachisaa ta'e waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_8::go: Sagalee waa'ee waan taatichi hojjechaa jirurratti baayyee barbaachisaa ta'ee waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_2::go: Sagalee waa'ee mana namichaa waan qabatamuu qabuu waraabi.
profile_interview_audio::clip_card_11::g: Sagalee waan qaamichi bashannanaaf godhuu waraabi.
